I've been thinking about Sunbird's invocation and Cascade for Maelstrom Wanderer, but they really don't interact that much. Casting your commander won't trigger SI, nor will any of Wanderer's cascade triggers, since they aren't cast from hand. It gets more interesting for Yidris, since the first spell you cast with cascade the trigger goes on the stack, but then so does SI's. I believe SI's trigger happens first since it technically goes on the stack last, I think.

so you can stack them
